OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 8 May to Sun 17 May
OL,6,FThere is a lot of uncertainty in the
OL,7,Fevolution through this period, more so
OL,8,Fthan normal, but overall it would
OL,9,Fappear that a rather unsettled theme
OL,10,Fis most likely. Most places are
OL,11,Ftherefore likely to see some rain or
OL,12,Fshowers at times, but also some drier,
OL,13,Fbrighter weather. The emphasis on
OL,14,Fwetter conditions may be more towards
OL,15,Fthe south at first, with low pressure
OL,16,Fperhaps more likely towards the south
OL,17,Fof the UK, before shifting further
OL,18,Fnorth later in the period as low
OL,19,Fpressure becomes more likely to set up
OL,20,Fto the north of the UK. Temperatures
OL,21,Fare likely to be near normal in the
OL,22,Fsouth throughout but on the cool side
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Fin the north at first before
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
OL,24,Frecovering to around normal later.
